data.title: Midshipman
data.meta_description:
His _17% career Black Type horses from starters_ continues to be among the best in the business - no stallion under $75k can top it. 

The only stallion with multiple juvenile Stakes winners at Saratoga in 2023.

Current three-year-olds include Stakes winners _Amidst Waves_, _Ship Cadet_, and _Midshipman's Dance_.
